{"tid":2360282,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"梅根哈利自傳滯銷　跌破1折乏人問津","createTime":"2021-01-09T15:04:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-11T01:33:41.000Z","uid":75656,"like":521,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":100,"replies":[{"pid":"9e79f28b979b96186f72dc5f4785730e61605c43","tid":2360282,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T15:04:44.000Z","msg":"英國哈利王子（Prince Harry）與妻子梅根馬可（Meghan Markle）育有1歲兒子亞契，他倆去年4月淡出皇室後仍受各界注目，以他們夫妻倆為主角的未授權傳記《尋找自由》（Finding Freedom）去年8月出版，當時售價20英鎊（約760元台幣），沒想到如今在拍賣網站只要0.99英鎊（約37元台幣）就可買到，還賣不出去。<br />\n<br />\n該書內容爆料小倆口的交往故事，包含5年前到非洲波札那的定情之旅，梅根對於在野外樹叢「野放」毫不扭捏，務實大方的態度讓哈利相當驚喜，對她的愛意更為深厚。<br />\n<br />\n顯然兩人離開英國後，讓英國民眾難以認同，過去發生什麼事也無人想知道，兩人愛的故事自然大跌價。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210108/2CRFIHHSCBBZRH2PBHIGAAQXHI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210108%2F2CRFIHHSCBBZRH2PBHIGAAQXHI%2F&d=3UqZ%2FPYEUq8PtOmaimGdDcTiFwqRwBg1VWT7Je45URE%3D&h=448502ba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210108%2F2CRFIHHSCBBZRH2PBHIGAAQXHI%2F&h=1861590b\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210108/2CRFIHHSCBBZRH2PBHIGAAQXHI/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">有無咁誇?會唔會只是咁岩搞特價，但台灣傳媒誇大左?</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbaf9880b849b4f2bd93363aed1382f504b5810e","tid":2360282,"uid":34869,"like":274,"dislike":2,"score":272,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T15:05:40.000Z","msg":"未授權傳記咁係邊個寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"043b2d553855b5002a6484f1b9e63d96649b1eab","tid":2360282,"uid":38904,"like":140,"dislike":3,"score":137,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T15:05:52.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">梅根對於在野外樹叢「野放」毫不扭捏</code></pre><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfe0ed508ba62170bc1a7f35f8ce585f432a794f","tid":2360282,"uid":331421,"l